FBIS4-58018 "drnes084_a_94001" FBIS-NES-94-084 Daily Report 30 Apr 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria Foreign Ministry Issues Statement on Yemen Events Foreign Ministry Issues Statement on Yemen Events LD3004203694 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 GMT 30 Apr 94 LD3004203694 Algiers ENTV Television Network Arabic BFN [Excerpt] [passage omitted] In a statement made by a spokesman for the Foreign Ministry, the Algerian authorities urge the parties to the conflict in Yemen to stop bloodshed in order to establish domestic peace and stick to dialogue to resolve the dispute and preserve the unity of Yemen. The statement further says that Algeria affirms its preparedness to continue mediation efforts whether at national level or in the framework of the mission entrusted to it by the last Arab Maghreb Union summit. The statement also says that Algeria regrets this internecine fighting and is following with concern the tragic events.
